opping of the initial <i>H-</i> and to her representation in art accompanied by a lamb. The colloquial form <i>Annes</i> led to some confusion with <i>Ann(e)</i> in earlier centuries. Frequent in the medieval period, the name was revived in the 19th century, and has been especially popular in Scotland.  See also  Annis ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Agnes was born in 1376. She had at least 1 daughter with Thomas Beauflour. She died in 1426, at the age of 50."},"et":{"1376–1426":"1376–1426","1373–1426":"1373–1426","1395–1466":"1395–1466","1426":"1426","1466":"1466","1376":"1376","1395":"1395","1373":"1373","about 1395":"umbes 1395","Gloucestershire, England":"Gloucestershire, England","of Bristol, Gloucestershire, England":"Bristol, Gloucestershire, England"},"fi":{"1376–1426":"1376–1426","1373–1426":"1373–1426","1395–1466":"1395–1466","1426":"1426","1466":"1466","1376":"1376","1395":"1395","1373":"1373","about 1395":"noin 1395","Gloucestershire, England":"Gloucestershire, England","of Bristol, Gloucestershire, England":"Bristol, Gloucestershire, England"},"fr":{"1376–1426":"1376–1426","1373–1426":"1373–1426","1395–1466":"1395–1466","1426":"1426","1466":"1466","1376":"1376","1395":"1395","1373":"1373","about 1395":"environ 1395","Gloucestershire, England":"Gloucestershire, Angleterre","of Bristol, Gloucestershire, England":"Bristol, Gloucestershire, Angleterre","lifeSummary":"Agnes est née en 1376. Elle a eu au moins 1 fille avec Thomas Beauflour. Elle est décédée en 1426, à l’âge de 50 ans."},"de":{"1376–1426":"1376–1426","1373–1426":"1373–1426","1395–1466":"1395–1466","1426":"1426","1466":"1466","1376":"1376","1395":"1395","1373":"1373","about 1395":"um 1395","Gloucestershire, England":"Gloucestershire, England","of Bristol, Gloucestershire, England":"Bristol, Gloucestershire, England","lifeSummary":"Agnes wurde 1376 geboren. Sie hatte mit Thomas Beauflour mindestens 1 Tochter. Sie starb 1426 im Alter von 50 Jahren."},"ht":{"1376–1426":"1376–1426","1373–1426":"